{"tid":642250,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"｛黃子華｝黃牛會唔會炒燶？","createTime":"2018-04-25T15:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T04:26:09.000Z","uid":86080,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"170d2d46474458d61e3f0c20c15accbddfbeb2bb","tid":642250,"uid":86080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"今次開26場，一場1.2萬個位，有30萬張飛左右。<br />\n公開發售雖然有15萬張飛，但好多比黃牛搶左，內部15萬都9成係比黃牛，即係黃牛有成15萬貨要散。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n內地討論度唔高，雖然都有廣東人買，但唔會好似其他明星演唱會（例如exo，五月天）咁瘋搶。講緊呢d演唱會都有黃牛門口殺價放飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfans好多都已經買到飛，買唔到飛又甘願比黃牛既人係唔係真係有成15萬人咁多呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃子華都叫我地唔放買黃牛，大家點解又要比黃牛賺？按而家巿價，佢一張都食幾百蚊，你甘心咩？<br />\n我知人人都好想睇，但只要大家忍下手，到時先買，黃牛成手貨，個價一定靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果黃牛被迫要低價放，扣埋排隊既人工都好多錢，同賣唔出果d，一定無咩水抽。<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一定要忍手啊！到時紅館門口等佢地跪住求我地買啦。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\nPs祝黃牛全家百病纏身，不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025bf57fa72ae172225f14cb3d367b888a5cf10f","tid":642250,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"有個事實係 支那好多人想睇<br />\n支那大手接貨 黃牛唔會蝕<br />\n<br />\n如果只限香港人睇既話 咁黃牛一定蝕到仆街<br />\n可惜唔會   <br />\n<br />\n立法實名制啦屌"},{"pid":"80f2dfe02aec7ce669b15935caedb20cfaf9c796","tid":642250,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:41:18.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"fb2ea087f9fa27ebf608b2230501ceb97d9c3c81","tid":642250,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"應該唔會，大把人買唔到<br />\n<br />\n利申：買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bab0d928401346364cf975b507ec11f2990f273","tid":642250,"uid":46192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"唔會, 睇淘寶勁多人買"},{"pid":"9c80662ffcac97fcef7077da6ffc305011aea31e","tid":642250,"uid":98811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:24:33.000Z","msg":"請珍惜黃牛黨"},{"pid":"ea887c6ef3b531d2d2f3386ce7218e4bcaa9835e","tid":642250,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c80662ffcac97fcef7077da6ffc305011aea31e","tid":642250,"uid":98811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:24:33.000Z","msg":"請珍惜黃牛黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"請珍惜炒價"}]}